                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6478" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9569 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">迷雾重重：“猪茅”失色是造假之过还是模式之伤</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The fog is thick: The fallen of &quot;zhumao&quot; is the fault of fraud or the flaw of model</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王旭，郝佳璐，赵梦菲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">牧原食品股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">牧原股份；超级猪周期；财务造假；重资产运营；2022百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Muyuan shares; Super pig cycle; Financial fraud; Heavy asset operation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">自2021年第四轮超级猪周期下行以来，一众生猪养殖企业陷入亏损，而有着强大积淀并伴随着超级猪周期上行所成长起来的牧原股份也频频遭到财务造假的质疑。牧原股份的财务数据是否存在水分？其大规模的融资扩张背后是否蕴藏着风险？本案例通过回顾了牧原股份的发展历程，讲述其从一间小小的猪舍，精心布局，精业笃行，并借着东风成长为行业龙头，一度被誉为“猪中茅台”，却又在行业寒冬中困于其运营模式的跌宕故事，以其遭到财务造假质疑事件为切入点，从牧原股份的运营模式、财务数据以及股价变化等方面来分析牧原股份在猪周期下行的行业背景下异常财务数据背后所蕴藏的风险，帮助学生理解异常财务数据现象背后的原因和可能带来的影响，提升学生风险意识和分析解决实际问题的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> Since the fourth round of super pig cycle downturn in 2021, a number of pig breeding enterprises have fallen into loss, and Mojihara Stock, which has a strong accumulation and grows up with the super pig cycle upturn, has been frequently questioned by financial fraud. Is there any moisture in the financial data of Makihara Shares? Is there a risk behind its massive expansion of financing? This case through reviews the developing course of the original stake, describe it from a small piggery, elaborate layout, conscientiousness relentlessly resourceful, and by dongfeng growth for the industry leading it, once known as the &quot;pigs in maotai&quot;, is trapped in its operating model in the industry of winter&#39;s dramatic story, with its financial fraud by questioning events as the breakthrough point, From grazing the operation mode of the original shares, financial data and stock price changes and so on to analyze the priest original stake in pig cycle downward under the background of abnormal financial data behind contain risk, help students to understand the reasons behind the phenomenon of abnormal financial data and the likely impact of, improve students&#39; risk consciousness and analysis ability to solve practical problems.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务报表分析》、《公司战略与风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">毛利率、资产周转率与运营模式的关系；关联交易合理性辨别；母子公司财务报表的联系；企业出现存贷双高现象的原因；信息不对称理论、信号传递理论；内部控制、风险管理；重资产运营模式的内涵与特征</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
